Package: survCleanr
Type: Package
Title: Prepare CDISC-Style Survival Analysis Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Tianlun",
           family = "Li",
           email = "your.email@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to prepare and clean survival analysis datasets 
    based on CDISC ADaM-style ADSL and ADTTE structures. Includes functions 
    for generating mock data, checking format requirements, merging covariates, 
    and outputting analysis-ready data for Kaplan-Meier or Cox models.
